### ========================================
###           SETTINGS ENDPOINTS
### ========================================
### Base URL: {{apiUrl}}/settings
### Todos requieren authGuard (cookies de sesión).
### ========================================

### ---------- GET SETTINGS ----------
### Obtiene la configuración actual del sistema.
GET {{apiUrl}}/settings

### ---------- UPDATE SETTINGS ----------
### Actualiza la configuración del sistema.
PUT {{apiUrl}}/settings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Mi POS System",
  "address": "Av. Siempre Viva 123",
  "phone": "555-1234",
  "tax_rate": 16.00,
  "low_stock_threshold": 10,
  "ticket_footer": "¡Gracias por su compra!"
}
